                <h1>4.5:80 (Page dimensions and margins)</h1>
                <p>The page dimensions for this document are 32 by 27. The default value for all margins is 0; consequently, there are no margin boxes.</p>
                <level2>
                    <h2>Changing page dimensions and margins within document</h2>
                    <p>Subsections in this subsection have their own designated page formats.</p>
                    <level3 id="narrow_page">
                        <h3>Narrower page</h3>
                        <p>This subsection uses a narrower page format (15 by 27).</p>
                    </level3>
                    <level3 id="short_page">
                        <h3>Shorter page</h3>
                        <p>This subsection uses a shorter page format (32 by 15).</p>
                    </level3>
                    <level3 id="wide_margins">
                        <h3>Wider margins</h3>
                        <p>This subsection uses the standard page format with wider margins (clockwise: 4 3 4 3).</p>
                    </level3>
                    <level3 id="narrow_page_with_margins">
                        <h3>Narrower page and wider margins</h3>
                        <p>This subsection uses the narrower page format with wider margins (clockwise: 3 1 3 2).</p>
                    </level3>
                </level2>
                <level2>
                    <h2>Adding page-margin boxes within document</h2>
                    <p>Subsections in this subsections have page-margin boxes.</p>
